  Spark is used for highly distributed design paralell  processing used across the clusters.
  
  When we submit the job using spark-submit then it initiallizes spark.context , then they allocated with the cluster manager.
  then executor launch on work nodes.
  
  User conversion code converted into the scheduler and break the job into the stages .
  
  Task assign to scheduler , if task fails spark rettry for another execution.
  
  After completing the job spark context shut down.
  
